      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="31147161">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/duyuhefei/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1235954-1.jpg" alt="独与鹤飞" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31147161/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31147161/" class="">第2305页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/duyuhefei/" class=" " title="独与鹤飞">独与鹤飞</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31147161">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">刘亮将二十骑平叛。城中叛军众至数万。亮先竖一纛于近城高岭，即驰入城中。叛军将领方置酒高会，卒见亮至，众皆骇愕。亮乃麾兵斩叛将，悬首州门，号令叛军。仍遥指城外纛，命二骑曰：出追大军。贼党凶惧，一时降服。北史2305 </span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-04-06 13:46</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                刘亮将二十骑平叛。城中叛军众至数万。亮先竖一纛于近城高岭，即驰入城中。叛军将领方置酒高会，卒见亮至，众皆骇愕。亮乃麾兵斩叛将，悬首州门，号令叛军。仍遥指城外纛，命二骑曰：出追大军。贼党凶惧，一时降服。北史2305 
